{"id":15189,"date":"2013-07-21T14:31:34","date_gmt":"2013-07-21T10:31:34","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=15189"},"modified":"2025-03-16T15:25:42","modified_gmt":"2025-03-16T11:25:42","slug":"salat-trail-pride-not-accepted","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/21\/salat-trail-pride-not-accepted\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Vanity: Prayer not accepted in trailing garments"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abu Huraira reported: While a man was praying with his garment draped below himself, the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>Go and perform ablution<\/strong>.\u201d The man went and performed ablution, then he came to the Prophet. The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Go and perform ablution<\/strong>.\u201d The man went and performed ablution, then he came back to the Prophet. Another man said to him, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, why did you order him to perform ablution again?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Verily, he was praying with his garment draped below himself. Allah Almighty does not accept the prayer of a man who drapes his garment<\/strong>.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 638<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Al-Nawawi<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0646\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u064e\u062c\u064f\u0644\u064c \u064a\u064f\u0635\u064e\u0644\u0650\u0651\u064a \u0645\u064f\u0633\u0652\u0628\u0650\u0644\u064b\u0627 \u0625\u0650\u0632\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0625\u0650\u0630\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\